{
  "description": {
    "title": "K-ETS forward transmission (lambda = 0.55) composed with a bank-threshold MSR",
    "paper": "PLANiT K-MSR working paper (July 2026), Sections 3/5 (lambda regimes); docs/forward-transmission.md (blend-then-clip order)",
    "composition": "Golden-scale complement to the unit anchor in tests/test_cap_rule_injection.py: the MSR (a supply operator) acts inside the COMPETITIVE COMPONENT of the lambda blend only (transmission.py module docstring; blocks-composition-rules.md R13/F3), reading the lagged participant bank. Hotelling component and the reserve floor are MSR-blind. Delivered price: P_t = max((1-lambda)*P_comp(t) + lambda*P_hot(t), floor).",
    "activation": "MSR bank_threshold under competitive needs banking_allowed: true + a non-myopic expectation rule (manual, V = 25,000 KRW) so Steel (100% freely allocated) banks its abatement surplus every year - the bank crosses msr_upper_threshold = 8 Mt after 2026 and the MSR withholds 12% of each auction from 2027 onward.",
    "inputs": "Cap 100 -> 82 Mt over 2026-2029 (KRW prices), auction derived from cap net of free allocation, flat auction reserve floor 12,000 KRW, carbon_budget = cap (Hotelling component budget), discount rate 5.5%.",
    "expected_output": {
      "delivered price, MSR scenario (2026-2029)": [
        12000.0,
        12819.21,
        14001.27,
        15197.57
      ],
      "delivered price, no-MSR scenario (2026-2029)": [
        12000.0,
        12000.0,
        12251.67,
        13739.57
      ],
      "static component, MSR vs no-MSR (2027)": [
        18036.0,
        13500.0
      ],
      "hotelling component (identical across scenarios, 2026-2029)": [
        8105.14,
        8550.92,
        9021.23,
        9517.39
      ],
      "reading": "2026 is floor-bound in BOTH scenarios (the floor is lambda- and MSR-immune: it clips AFTER the blend). The MSR withholding raises the competitive component (2027: 18,036 vs 13,500 KRW; delta = withheld 5.04 Mt x 900 KRW/Mt on the residual demand slope), lifting the delivered price off the floor a full year earlier than without the MSR. The MSR's own diagnostics live in the component solve - the delivered-path MSR columns read 0 by construction (transmission.py:_evaluate_at_prices)."
    },
    "run": "PYTHONPATH=src .venv/bin/python -m ets.cli --config examples/k_ets_lambda_msr.json"
  },
